WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.000
Apple just rolled out iOS seventeen point four point one,

00:00:03.001 --> 00:00:06.081
just two weeks after 17.4 hit our devices.

00:00:06.082 --> 00:00:06.841
But what's new?

00:00:06.842 --> 00:00:08.441
Apple's keeping it under wraps,

00:00:08.442 --> 00:00:11.821
stating only important bug fixes and security updates.

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.480
Many of you have been reporting issues like animation freezes,

00:00:15.481 --> 00:00:17.421
AirPods not connecting properly,

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:19.160
unexpected battery drains,

00:00:19.161 --> 00:00:21.141
and trouble with Bluetooth and Wi-Fi.

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:22.960
If you've been having any of these issues,

00:00:22.961 --> 00:00:24.561
this update might be your fix.

00:00:24.562 --> 00:00:28.241
It's recommended for all users so updating can smooth these bugs out.

00:00:28.242 --> 00:00:29.241
If you like the video,

00:00:29.242 --> 00:00:32.160
please give it a thumbs up and follow for more iOS insights.
